    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🏏 Cricket Match Intelligence — Workflow D\n\n**Runs:** Daily at 7:30 AM AEST (21:30 UTC) — 30 min before Workflow A\n\n**What it does:**\n1. Fetches workflow config from DB settings\n2. Fetches current/upcoming matches from CricAPI\n3. Filters for Australian-relevant matches\n4. If match found → POSTs isMatchDay=true + match details to /api/cricket-matches\n5. If no match → POSTs isMatchDay=false\n6. If match day → sends Telegram alert\n\n**Workflow A fetches /api/cricket-matches** at 8:00 AM.\nIf isMatchDay=true → generates BOTH daily theme post AND match day post (2 PENDING posts)\n\n**Storage:** PostgreSQL via /api/cricket-matches\n\n**Env vars required in n8n:**\n- CRICAPI_KEY",
